* <a href="https://ukgovernmentdfe.slack.com/archives/CLE46M53L" target="_blank">Manchester: #mcr-userresearchers</a>
* <a href="https://ukgovernmentdfe.slack.com/archives/C03NGLQDJJW" target="_blank">Sheffield: #sheffield_user_researchers</a>
